It seems that it's caused by this rule:
```
timeanddate.com#$##naw, .header__inner { position: static !important; }
```
from `Web Annoyances Ultralist`.
Temporary solution:
```
timeanddate.com#@$##naw, .header__inner { position: static !important; }
```

@yourduskquibbles Could you please take a look?
